name: CompositeMap_getTest
description: Unit tests for the get method of the CompositeMap class.

test_cases.name: testGetExistingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method for existing keys in the CompositeMap.

test_cases.name: testGetNonExistingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method for a non-existing key in the CompositeMap.

test_cases.name: testGetAfterAddingNewMap
test_cases.description: Tests the get method after adding a new map to the CompositeMap.

test_cases.name: testGetAfterRemovingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method after removing a key from the CompositeMap.

test_cases.name: testGetAfterPuttingNewKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method after putting a new key-value pair in the CompositeMap.

test_cases.name: testGetAfterPuttingExistingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method after updating an existing key-value pair in the CompositeMap.

test_cases.name: testGetWithNullKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with a null key in the CompositeMap.

test_cases.name: testGetWithEmptyCompositeMap
test_cases.description: Tests the get method on an empty CompositeMap.

test_cases.name: testGetWithSingleMap
test_cases.description: Tests the get method on a CompositeMap with a single map.

test_cases.name: testGetWithMultipleMaps
test_cases.description: Tests the get method on a CompositeMap with multiple maps.

test_cases.name: testGetWithOverlappingKeys
test_cases.description: Tests the get method on a CompositeMap with overlapping keys.
